dct_title_s: Street, address, and block guide Princeton Borough & Princeton Township / published by Gerald Breese
dct_description_sm: Map shows borough, township, and arbitrary block boundaries, block information; streets; and roads. "Map adapted from Official 1968 Township map." Verso: Location of streets and street address numbers. "This map of Princeton Borough and Princeton Township is current as June 1, 1968. The first such map and guide were originally prepared as research and analysis tools, and were part of a publication prepared by Gerald Breese". Bureau of Urban Research, Princeton NJ. "Map adapted from Official 1968 Township map." Verso: Location of streets and street address numbers. Companion text: Princeton block coding guide: A location index for distributing research data by blocks in Princeton Borough and Princeton Township, New Jersey / Gerald William Breese. Princeton, NJ: Bureau of Urban Research, Princeton University. 1956. The Map Library does not have a copy of this title.
dct_publisher_sm: Princeton, N.J. : Bureau of Urban Research, Princeton University, 1968.
